name: DEUSEXMACHINA
description:
DEUS EX MACHINA
ἀπὸ μηχανῆς θεός
god out of the machine

DEUSEXMACHINA is a god introduced by means of a crane in ancient Greek and Roman drama to decide the final outcome a person or thing. Is a plot device whereby a seemingly unsolvable problem in a story is suddenly and abruptly resolved by an unexpected and unlikely occurrence.

this analog collage was a key piece of my work with images in 2015. Is when you are absent of your body with distractions and the bomb can gonna catch you. it's a behavior of the life, in your eternal mouvement. in my way just the dream
